  Locus:
    Page: 454
    Verse: 2
Tags:
  - Suffering
---
Suffering gives us the impetus to escape from our self-limiting ignorance.
If God did not send these gifts of suffering and misery, many people would be
content to live their whole lives alienated from God and ignorant of their
true nature.
